### Key Material Information (Buy-Back Announcement):  
- **Buy-Back Type:** Other buy-back (Nasdaq-listed Class A & B common stock repurchase program).  
- **Total Authorized Repurchase:**  
  - **2021 Program:** Up to **US$1 billion** (remaining ~**US$698.2M** spent as of **17/07/2025**).  
  - **2025 Program:** Additional **US$1 billion** authorized.  
- **Latest Daily Activity (17/07/2025):**  
  - **Shares Repurchased:** 5,373 Class B shares.  
  - **Consideration Paid:** **US$186,013.26** (avg. price **~US$34.62**).  
- **Price Range (Historical):** **US$15.17** (low, 2022) to **US$35.41** (high, 15/07/2025).  
- **Broker:** Morgan Stanley.  
- **CDIs Excluded:** No ASX-listed CDIs will be repurchased.  

*Note: No impact on ASX-listed securities; Nasdaq-focused program.*
